Key Verses

Reverend Walter Johnson

Come See!

Reverend Walter Johnson is a long time resident of Conshohocken. As a child growing up in Conshohocken his mother provided him a strong spiritual base.

Walter Johnson has been the guest pastor at St. Paul's since 2005.
